{"tid":2163231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★同舟口罩製造商鬧糾紛　工程師聲稱投資後伙伴更改協議　現求賠償","createTime":"2020-08-18T14:05:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T14:06:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6ee75efafe179103e2757ddacf59fe6fd44915","tid":2163231,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"生產「同舟」口罩的瑞士億科，遭一名工程師入稟循民事控告。該名工程師聲稱和瑞士億科等合作生產口罩，並申請政府的本地口罩生產資助計劃，工程師指根據他們的協議，每年獲利最多可達5400萬元。惟其他合作伙伴涉過橋抽板，在工程師投放逾430萬元後，郤私下更改協議。他們又指工程師提供的生產設備不合規格，毋需遵從之前的協議。工程師昨(17日)入稟高等法院，向瑞士億科等索償。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/512551/%E5%90%8C%E8%88%9F%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%95%86%E9%AC%A7%E7%B3%BE%E7%B4%9B-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%BE%8C%E4%BC%99%E4%BC%B4%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%8F%BE%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F512551%2F%25E5%2590%258C%25E8%2588%259F%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E9%25AC%25A7%25E7%25B3%25BE%25E7%25B4%259B-%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A8%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%258A%2595%25E8%25B3%2587%25E5%25BE%258C%25E4%25BC%2599%25E4%25BC%25B4%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2594%25B9%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E7%258F%25BE%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%25B3%25A0%25E5%2584%259F&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5hjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=4de4f938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/512551/%E5%90%8C%E8%88%9F%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%A3%BD%E9%80%A0%E5%95%86%E9%AC%A7%E7%B3%BE%E7%B4%9B-%E5%B7%A5%E7%A8%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%81%B2%E7%A8%B1%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%BE%8C%E4%BC%99%E4%BC%B4%E6%9B%B4%E6%94%B9%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%8F%BE%E6%B1%82%E8%B3%A0%E5%84%9F</a>"},{"pid":"f7c45bf026f967a21a98626af7e833c5cf05b619","tid":2163231,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"